name: CHINESE ROOM #3
description:
From the series "Chinese Room". 

Image created by me in interaction with Artificial Intelligence used as a painting tool.

The name "Chinese Room" refers to the famous argument of the philosopher John Searle. The "Chinese Room" argument holds that a computer executing a program cannot have a "mind", "understanding" or "consciousness", regardless of how intelligently or human-like the program may make the computer behave.
